="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>The End of the End of History</em></a><em> </em>(2021).</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-2f963901-8 dqFLeN"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/samhaselby" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 iTsAjg">Sam Haselby</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-8abcc030-0 koSWWJ"><span>6,400<!-- --> words</span><div class="group z-10 inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1 sm:hidden"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="flex-shrink-0 font-sans">Save</span></div></div><br/><div class="mx-0 my-5 [grid-area:syndication] print:hidden max-sm:hidden"><a class="inline-flex bg-grey-light-bg p-5 text-center font-mono text-grey-mid text-xs leading-relaxed tracking-widest duration-200 hover:bg-black hover:text-white" href="/syndication?article_slug=what-will-an-evangelical-brazil-look-like&amp;article_name=Utopia brasileira&amp;author=Alex Hochuli&amp;date=7 November 2024">SYNDICATE THIS <!-- -->ESSAY</a></div><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 iontxq sc-2f963901-10 kVaaOI"><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 iontxq"><div><br/></div><div class="sc-809612e0-0 fYECoZ"><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-809612e0-1 kdkgPH"><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6zm-2 0l-8 5-8-5h16zm0 12H4V8l8 5 8-5v10z"></path></svg><span class="sc-809612e0-2 cmbDHE font-sans">Email</span></div><div class="group z-10 inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20" height="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7