><p class="sc-c0f26063-3 dwDZqP font-mono peer-hover:hidden">essay</p><p class="sc-c0f26063-2 cA-dtSP font-mono peer-hover:hidden">Food and drink</p></div><p class="m-x-0 mt-3.5 mb-3 font-bold font-serif text-[25px] leading-[1.2] [grid-area:title] sm:text-[28px]">The flavour of mechanisation</p><p class="mt-0 mb-3.5 text-base leading-normal tracking-normal [grid-area:standfirst]">Olive oil was revered and cherished by the ancients. But its distinctive peppery taste is really a modern invention</p><p class="sc-c0f26063-0 sc-c0f26063-8 Yva-Dw jfoikg">Massimo Mazzotti</p></div><div class="sc-c0f26063-4 gLchsi"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/india-is-a-postcolonial-power-its-rule-in-kashmir-is-colonial"><div class="sc-c0f26063-7 hKgpRs"><div type="essay" class="sc-31fe189a-2 hIkfIs"><img alt="Photo of a soldier in camouflage standing on a busy market street surrounded by people and colourful fabrics." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/6c48f3dd-92d4-4930-82bc-3f7b267a079e/essay-v2-panos_00091961.jpg?width=1